SPEAKER_00: In shop drawings, it became two shorter rods, easier to build.

4
00:00:16,198 --> 00:00:17,561
SPEAKER_00: But the load path changed.

5
00:00:18,222 --> 00:00:22,088
SPEAKER_00: The fourth floor connection now carried both walkways, not one.

6
00:00:22,850 --> 00:00:24,772
SPEAKER_00: The load essentially doubled.

7
00:00:24,888 --> 00:00:44,432
SPEAKER_00: nbs later found the original design was already weak the revision left roughly one-third of code expected capacity on july 17 1981 two walkways collapsed during a crowded dance official records count 113 dead and 186 injured

8
